                     <interp inst="t17840526-96-person864" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I took him with the handkerchief under his arm, they were both together.</p>
               <p>PRISONER MORGAN's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I can tell where I had been, and who is my master; my master's name is Gordon, in Petty France, he is a plaisterer, I had been at work in Brook-street; I know nothing of that young man.</p>
               <p>BOTH <rs id="t17840526-96-verdict434" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17840526-96-verdict434" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
